data.description: SELLER HAS ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 3.0%.....Seller financing available. Welcome to Villaggio Reserve, a premier 55+ community. This 2BR/2BA home, complete with an office/den, has a lot to offer. Relax on the screened lanai with no back neighbors for added privacy. The kitchen impresses with granite counters, maple cabinets, an island, and stainless steel appliances, including a double oven.  The master suite is a treat with two walk-in closets and a bathroom that features a tub, separate shower, and two sinks. The home also has hurricane-impact windows for safety. Living in Villaggio Reserve means access to a modern clubhouse, pools, spa, cafe, gym, tennis, pickleball courts, bocce, and game rooms. Experience comfortable living in a vibrant setting.
